<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.5.8">
<l>namakkum pūviṉmicai naṅkaikku miṉpaṉai ñālattār</l>
<l>tamakkum vāṉat tavarkkum perumāṉai taṇṭāmarai</l>
<l>cumakkum pātap perumāṉaic coṉmālaikaḷ collumā</l>
<l>ṟamaikka vallēṟ kiṉiyāvar nikarakal vāṉattē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who is a pleasure to us and to the girl on the flower, the great lord</l>
<l>of those in the world and those in heaven, the great lord with feet</l>
<l>that bear cool lotuses, to me, who is able to create a way to speak</l>
<l>word garlands on him, who is now equal in wide heaven?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
